Route: /users/:username
- Passes the following data to the view:

0) name:			Full name of the requested user.
1) userName:		User name of the requested user.
2) numberOfFollowers:	Number of followers the requested user has.
3) numberOfPosts:		The number of posts the requested user  has made.
4) profilePic: 		URL to the profile pic of the requested user
5) profileColor:		the navbar color for the currently logged in user
6) isCurrentUser: 		Whether the profile being requested is of the currently logged in User.
7) currentUsername: 	The user name of the currently logged in user
8) numberOfFollowing:	the number of users following the viewed profile
9) profileDescription: The description of the viewed profile.
